1. *Večno* ćeš ostati u mom srcu. (You will *always* remain in my heart.)
2. U potrazi za *večnom* ljubavi. (In search of *eternal* love.)
3. Spreman sam da *večno* ostanem tvoj. (I'm ready to remain yours *forever*.)
4. *Večno* pitanje ljudskog postojanja. (*Eternal* question of human existence.)
5. Njihova ljubav je *večna*. (Their love is *eternal*.)
6. *Večna* ti slava i hvala! (*Eternal* glory and thanks to you!)
7. *Večnom* slavom ovjenčan. (Adorned with *eternal* glory.)
8. Zauvek i *večno* zajedno. (Together forever and *everlasting*.)
9. Ovo je *večno* pitanje našeg vremena. (This is the *perennial* question of our time.)
10. Neka joj je *večna* slava. (May she have *eternal* glory.)

Note: The word "večno" is translated as "eternal" or "forever" in English.